<br>
Take it up with someone who gives a fuck.  I cannot see how the use of the argument &quot;I am right because you are Flabello and/or Pneumatic&quot; holds water, if you wish to defend your point of the argument how about delivering a quantifyable argument rather than saying &quot;your a fucktard and I dont like you&quot;.<br>
<br>
My argument was that if the monster should be worth 6% xp to kill solo then it should be given that value for an un-grouped soloer and a solo-grouper.  The value should be 6% regardless of this exploit or not.  Otherwise the xp value of the mob is not fair for those playing at a time when there are not a divisable by 6 number of soloer's to hand which to me doesn't seem fair or correct.<br>
<br>
Fault that please, not who you know/think/want me to be.<br>
