<br>
&quot;Dear Tyan:<br>
<br>
Thank you for pointing this out to us.  We reviewed this information and for a couple of weeks now we have been trying this out on the test server.  Yes, we can see now that this could be used as an exploit.<br>
<br>
However, there are some good points to be made to keep the experience table in place.  I had a meeting with the team this morning and we came up with the only answer we could.  We are going to nerf wizards again.<br>
<br>
Sincerely,<br>
